Installation Instructions
*************************

1. If you have AMD cards download and install AMD APP SDK for your Linux platform from:
	http://developer.amd.com/tools/heterogeneous-computing/amd-accelerated-parallel-processing-app-sdk/downloads/

2. Run:		
	./configure

3.	Run:
		make
	or
		make CPPFLAGS=-DUCFG_TRC=1			# enable tracing

4. Optionally run:
	make install


If the program don't find OpenCL.so run it as:
LD_LIBRARY_PATH=$AMDAPPSDKROOT/lib/x86 ./coin-miner


